■詳細説明

The Gunner Waterproof Jacket is constructed from a polymer reinforced textile durable outer shell and incorporates a 100% waterproof inner lining to ensure maximum riding comfort. With its removable thermal lining and CE certified protection this jacket is ideal for the rigors of sport touring - whatever the weather.
・GUNNER WATERPROOF JACKET KEY FEATURES:・Durable polymer-coated 600 Dernier textile for superb water-repelling performance.・100% waterproof and breathable lining for high levels of comfort and weather protection.・Featuring Alpinestars Climate Control System: strategically positioned zippered front air intakes and rear exhaust to help regulate internal body temperature.・Removable long-sleeve thermal liner with poly-fabric collar ensures jacket versatility and comfort in cold and hot conditions.・Class-leading, CE-certified elbow and shoulder protectors for added impact protection.・Chest and Back protector compartments with advanced poly-foam comfort padding (CE-certified Bio-Armor back protector insert available as accessory).・Soft poly-fabric comfort edge around collar.・Velcro® sleeve volume adjustment system and gusseted Velcro® cuff adjustment for improved riding fit.・Velcro® waistband and collar allows for highly personalized and secure fit while in various riding positions.・Extended and reinforced lower back for riding comfort.・Pre-curved sleeves for improved comfort and performance in the riding position.・External hand pockets, plus internal pockets and waterproof wallet pocket; pockets are zipped for peace-of-mind closure.

他のカラーリングはこちら

■詳細説明
心地良い暖かさの秘密。反射熱と身体の芯から暖める電熱のダブル効果。
1.体の芯から暖める！
暖まりに瞬発力はありませんが、ヒーターから発する遠赤外線を超遠赤外線（テラヘルツ）に変換することで「心地良い暖かさ」を実現しました。
2.アルミ蒸着シートで熱を反射！
ヒーターから外側へ逃げてしまう熱を反射することで熱効率と保温性を高めています。
3.省エネ設計！
省エネ設計のセミコンヒーターを採用。
持続力があり、暖かさ長持ち。ゴワツキにくく着心地が良い。
折り曲げに強く、断線しにくいところもメリットです。
・接続時間目安
弱：約4.5時間（約9時間）
中：約3.5時間（約7時間）
強：約2.5時間（約4時間）
※モバイルバッテリー（91480/別売品）1個使用時、カッコ内は2個使用時の接続時間目安です。
・電源は、モバイルバッテリー（別売）と車体電源（別売）の2WAY方式！
1.別売のバッテリーを内側の専用ポケットに入れ、USB接続します。（最大2個まで接続可能で、接続時間を延ばせます）
2.USB延長ケーブル（別売）を使用することで、オートバイの電源取り出しソケットから電力を確保できます。
※USBケーブルは運転の妨げにならないよう調整してください。

■詳細説明

A highly versatile adventure touring jacket constructed from an abrasion and tear-resistant poly-fabric, the Bogota Jacket features Alpinestars exclusive DRYSTAR® membrane for guaranteed waterproofing. This jacket also features innovative ventilation systems as well as superb levels of protection thanks to its integrated CE-certified elbow and shoulder protectors.
BOGOTA DRYSTAR® JACKET KEY FEATURES:・Multi-material construction with a highly abrasion and tear resistant poly-fabric main shell and multi-panel mesh lining for comfort and durability.・Removable and interchangeable waterproof and breathable DRYSTAR® full liner with taped seams to ensure long term water-repelling performance.・Long sleeve thermal liner (100g on body, 80g on sleeves) ensures jacket versatility and comfort in cold and hot conditions and can be fully removed with easy identification red zippers and integrated stretch comfort edge.・Removable CE-certified shoulder and elbow protection for superb impact protection.・Chest and back pad compartments with PE padding (Alpinestars Bionic chest pads and Back Armor available as accessory upgrade).・Anatomical, pre-curved sleeve design incorporate Velcro® volume control adjustment straps for improved comfort, precision adjustment of garment and to help keep elbow protections in place.・Jet Ventilation System (JVS): strategically positioned zippered air intakes on torso with rear air exhaust vent on upper back for cooling performance on long rides.・Climate Control System (CCS) on sleeves incorporates mesh gussets and zipper closures for improved levels of ventilation control.・Four external front pockets for convenient storage, including two waterproof pockets and two large cargo pockets, plus external large rear utility pocket. Internal pockets are waterproof and zippered for peace-of-mind closure.・Collar construction incorporates comfort lining and features Velcro® closure and strap garage to allow collar to be securely kept in place while open.・Fine-tuned fit afforded by D-ring waist adjustment for a secure, personalized fit while riding.・Extended profile lower back for riding comfort for extra protection in the lumbar region.・Reflective detailing on front and back improves rider visibility.・Two internal waist connection zippers (on main shell and on DRYSTAR membrane) for attachment to Alpinestars riding pants.・Premium YKK zips used throughout.

■注意点
※画像には他のカラーリングが含まれています。

■詳細説明

The Gunner Waterproof Jacket is constructed from a polymer reinforced textile durable outer shell and incorporates a 100% waterproof inner lining to ensure maximum riding comfort. With its removable thermal lining and CE certified protection this jacket is ideal for the rigors of sport touring - whatever the weather.
・GUNNER WATERPROOF JACKET KEY FEATURES:・Durable polymer-coated 600 Dernier textile for superb water-repelling performance.・100% waterproof and breathable lining for high levels of comfort and weather protection.・Featuring Alpinestars Climate Control System: strategically positioned zippered front air intakes and rear exhaust to help regulate internal body temperature.・Removable long-sleeve thermal liner with poly-fabric collar ensures jacket versatility and comfort in cold and hot conditions.・Class-leading, CE-certified elbow and shoulder protectors for added impact protection.・Chest and Back protector compartments with advanced poly-foam comfort padding (CE-certified Bio-Armor back protector insert available as accessory).・Soft poly-fabric comfort edge around collar.・Velcro® sleeve volume adjustment system and gusseted Velcro® cuff adjustment for improved riding fit.・Velcro® waistband and collar allows for highly personalized and secure fit while in various riding positions.・Extended and reinforced lower back for riding comfort.・Pre-curved sleeves for improved comfort and performance in the riding position.・External hand pockets, plus internal pockets and waterproof wallet pocket; pockets are zipped for peace-of-mind closure.
